devdoc.author: Abdullah Jabbar
devdoc.details: A decentralized todo list application with gas-optimized operations

bytes32ToString(bytes32).details: Convert bytes32 to string (for displaying categories)

clearAllTasks().details: Emergency function to clear all tasks (if needed)

params._category: Task category as string (converted to bytes32)

deleteTask(uint256).details: Delete a task (marks as deleted by moving last task to deleted position)

getAllTasks().details: Get all tasks for the caller

getTask(uint256).details: Get a specific task by ID

getTaskStats().details: Get task statistics for the user

returns._0: Array of filtered tasks with their IDs

params._completed: Whether to get completed or pending tasks

returns._0: Array of filtered tasks with their IDs
